'''朱迪斯·赫林'''（{{lang-en|Judith Herrin}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|ɛr|ɪ|n}}，{{bd|1942年|}}）是一位[[英国|英国]][[考古学|考古学]]家，主攻[[古典时代晚期|古典时代晚期]]与[[拜占庭學|拜占庭學]]<ref name="WSJByzantium">{{cite news |url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704615504576172512424600444 |title=The Glories of Byzantium |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |date=12 March 2011 |access-date=24 December 2016 |archive-date=2017-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518033609/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052748704615504576172512424600444 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，为[[伦敦国王学院|伦敦国王学院]]资深研究员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kclpure.kcl.ac.uk/portal/judith.herrin.html|title=KCL research portal|access-date=22 February 2017|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820221649/https://kclpure.kcl.ac.uk/portal/judith.herrin.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要作品有《拜占庭：一个中世纪帝国的传奇历史》（''Byzantium: The Surprising Life of a Medieval Empire''）等。

